725500f-a.title: Queens: 59th Avenue - 59th Street
725500f-a.text:
Fifty-ninth Ave., north side, east of 59th Street (right, not
shown), showing one of a group of Cord Meyers' houses. Bis property
extended as far north as Grand Ave., west as far as the Long Island
Railroad, south as far as 59th Road, and east as far as 59th Place.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
